How to build a debian package for lcg-info: 
  
1. Create the following directory structure: 
  
debian/ 
    |__ lcg-infosites/
               |  
               |__ DEBIAN/ 
                        |__ control 
               |__ usr/  
                      |__bin/ 
                           |__ lcg_infosites 
                      |  
                      |__ share/ 
                              | 
                              |__doc/  
                                   |__ copyright 
                                   | 
                                   |__ changelog 
                              | 
                              |__ man/ 
                                    | 
                                    |__ man1/ 
                                           |__ lcg-infosites.1 
  
2. Run: dpkg-deb --build lcg-infosites

3. Rename lcg-infosites.deb to the right version lcg-infosites-x.y.z-r.deb 

